  "prompt": "Which are the best IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi?",
  "response": "As of my last update in 2023, these are some of the well-regarded IELTS coaching institutes in Delhi:\n\n1. **British Council**:\n   - Offers IELTS preparation courses with experienced trainers.\n   - Known for its comprehensive study material and practice tests.\n\n2. **Jamboree Education**:\n   - Offers specialized IELTS coaching with personalized attention.\n   - Provides extensive practice sessions and mock tests.\n\n3. **Manya - The Princeton Review**:\n   - Known for its structured program and skilled trainers.\n   - Offers personalized coaching and resources to improve score.\n\n4. **Megamind Consultants**:\n   - Provides tailored coaching for IELTS with experienced faculty.\n   - Offers regular mock tests and feedback sessions.\n\n5. **Fateh Education**:\n   - Offers detailed and interactive IELTS preparation classes.\n   - Provides extensive practice materials and test tips.\n\n6. **Gateway Abroad**:\n   - Renowned for its focused approach and expert guidance.\n   - Offers comprehensive study materials and regular assessments.\n\n7. **Plutus Academy**:\n   - Known for its expert faculty and focused coaching.\n   - Provides detailed study plans and continuous assessment.\n\nBefore choosing an institute, it's important to consider factors such as faculty experience, batch size, course duration, fee structure, and location. Additionally, reading reviews and possibly attending demo classes can provide better insight into the quality of coaching.",
